Form Widgets
===============

This document is a list of available :term:`ODK Collect` :term:`form` :term:`widgets <widget>` (question types), with:

- examples images from the ODK Collect app
- example Excel spreadsheet rows for creating form widgets with :term:`ODK XLSForm`
- example :term:`ODK XForm` XML snippets

.. _string-input:

String Input
--------------

A simple text input.

.. image:: /img/form-widgets/string-input.*
  :alt: String input form widget, displayed in ODK Collect on an Android phone. The label is "What is your full name?"
  :class: device-screen-vertical

XLSForm Rows
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

.. csv-table:: survey
  :header: type, name, label, required

  string, full_name, What is your full name?, true()


XForm XML
~~~~~~~~~~~~

.. code-block:: xml

  <bind nodeset="/odk-example-form/full_name" required="true()" type="string"/>

  <input ref="/odk-example-form/full_name">
    <label>What is your full name?</label>
  </input>

.. _single-select:

Single Select
----------------

A radio-button single choice from several options.

.. image:: /img/form-widgets/single-select.*
  :alt: Single-select (radio button) form widget, displayed in ODK Collect on an Android phone.
  :class: device-screen-vertical

XLSForm Rows
~~~~~~~~~~~~~

.. csv-table:: survey
  :header: type, name, label, hint

  select_one organizations,	organization,	What organization do you work for?, "If your organization is not in this list, select other, you will get a free text box where you can specify."

.. csv-table:: choices
  :header: list_name, name, label

  organizations, amf, Against Malaria Foundation
  organizations, gd, Give Directly
  organizations, sci, Schistosomiasis Control Initiative
  organizations, dwi, Deworm the World Initiative
  organizations, other, Other. Continue to next question to specify.

The ``list_name`` in the **choices** table matches the string *after* ``select_one`` in the ``type`` column of the **survey** table.


XForm XML
~~~~~~~~~~~~

.. code-block:: xml

  <select1 ref="/odk-example-form/organization">
    <label>What organization do you work for?</label>
    <hint>If your organization is not in this list, select other, you will get a free text box where you can specify.</hint>
    <item>
      <label>Against Malaria Foundation</label>
      <value>amf</value>
    </item>
    <item>
      <label>Give Directly</label>
      <value>gd</value>
    </item>
    <item>
      <label>Schistosomiasis Control Initiative</label>
      <value>sci</value>
    </item>
    <item>
      <label>Deworm the World Initiative</label>
      <value>dwi</value>
    </item>
    <item>
      <label>Other. Continue to next question to specify.</label>
      <value>other</value>
    </item>
  </select1>
